{"tid":2517362,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"《鬼滅之刃》紅遍全球！日本電影睽違22年再登美票房冠軍","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:45:44.000Z","uid":25345,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"abf979001e42af9bc28f88d11a7bbf4f9663efd1","tid":2517362,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/571/60924e9d61763.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F571%2F60924e9d61763.jpg&h=29a79dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本人氣漫畫改編的電影《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》不僅在台日創下票房佳績，4月23日在美國上映後，首週便賣破當地外語電影票房紀錄，這也是日本電影睽違22年，再度稱霸美國票房。<br />\n<br />\n漫畫《鬼滅之刃》實體書在全球賣破1億本，而動畫版在Netflix上播出後，更是在各地引起「鬼滅旋風」，《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》則是接續動畫版之後的劇情，去年10月上映後，迅速成為日本新一代票房冠軍，打破已經雄霸寶座20年的《神隱少女》。<br />\n<br />\n而據日媒報導，上月23日《鬼滅之刃劇場版無限列車篇》在美國上映後，首週週末票房便更新美國的外語電影票房紀錄；上映第二週週末光是4月30日至5月2日，短短三天票房便高達640萬美元（約新台幣1億8054萬元），登上當地週末電影票房冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n這也是繼1999年的《寶可夢電影版：超夢的逆襲》後，日本電影睽違22年再度稱霸美國電影票房。事實上，美國現在仍處於防疫限制的狀況，人們要自由進出電影院看電影不是易事，能創下此等佳績，可見《鬼滅之刃》的人氣難以抵擋。"},{"pid":"7935f19eeaabc84386b87580555729d847fc5a2b","tid":2517362,"uid":187192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:27:27.000Z","msg":"連登仔:垃圾 疫情無野睇先睇 唔係UFO有鬼人睇....."},{"pid":"42cfa349e0b06584a31ab22ee997fdea4756dc6c","tid":2517362,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"大哥沒有輸"},{"pid":"2d3be94fbfcdd21ba5011934c7d98af4c21c9f6e","tid":2517362,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"42cfa349e0b06584a31ab22ee997fdea4756dc6c","tid":2517362,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:32:58.000Z","msg":"大哥沒有輸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:35:04.000Z","msg":"真係好感人呢段<br />\n哭撚左😭"},{"pid":"7f81e97e99826ef9a183ec13c94758001f466ced","tid":2517362,"uid":168513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:42:31.000Z","msg":"鬼滅世一  大哥沒有舒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"231f2374131aad78bb20a48c20578ce3ad5fcbc6","tid":2517362,"uid":170786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:43:54.000Z","msg":"等睇傻鳩入來盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d0a15f0a6c13cac0fcde9fe59c588718995c23","tid":2517362,"uid":48362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:45:44.000Z","msg":"ufo <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}